《minecraft Minecraft） it is a sandbox video game, pioneered by marcus alexey poisson ( Notch）。 game by Mojang Studios maintenance, now affiliated to microsoft Xbox game studio. the game was originally held on may 17, 2009 as Classic the version was released and released on november 18, 2011 Java official version. minecraft gaming platforms include desktop devices, mobile devices and game consoles. the chinese version is now represented by netease games and operated in mainland china on may 20, 2016 [34]。
from its inception to jens bergenstein ( Jeb） before joining and taking charge of development, almost all the development work in minecraft was Notch finish. game music by daniel rosenfield ( C418） and lena renne ( Lena Raine） creation; christopher zetstrand draws the paintings in the game. the game is themed on the player’s freedom to create and destroy different kinds of blocks in a three-dimensional space filled with blocks. players can play single in the game person or more person in mode, you can destroy or create exquisite buildings and art, or collect items to explore maps to complete the game's achievements (progress). players can also try playing methods such as redstone circuits and commands in creative mode (turn on cheating). 
2019in may, minecraft defeated tetris and sold 176 million copies, becoming the best-selling video game of all time.  [48]。2020in 2020, "minecraft" won the "2020 children's choice award"  [44]。2023in october 2019, "minecraft" sold more than 300 million copies ]。
2024in november 2024, he won the 2024 golden rocker award for continuing games ( PC/host).
school_gallery.chinese_prompt:
《我的世界》（Minecraft）是一款沙盒类电子游戏，开创者为马库斯·阿列克谢·泊松（Notch）。游戏由Mojang Studios维护，现隶属于微软Xbox游戏工作室。游戏最初于2009年5月17日作为Classic版本发布，并于2011年11月18日发布Java正式版。我的世界的游戏平台囊括桌面设备、移动设备和游戏主机。中国版现由网易游戏代理，于2016年5月20日在中国大陆运营 [34]。
自开创伊始到延斯·伯根斯坦（Jeb）加入并负责开发之前，我的世界几乎全部的开发工作由Notch完成。游戏音乐由丹尼尔·罗森菲尔德（C418）和莉娜·雷恩（Lena Raine）创作；克里斯托弗·泽特斯特兰绘制了游戏中的画。该游戏以玩家在一个充满着方块的三维空间中自由地创造和破坏不同种类的方块为主题。玩家在游戏中可以在单人或多人模式中通过摧毁或创造精妙绝伦的建筑物和艺术，或者收集物品探索地图以完成游戏的成就（进度）。玩家也可以尝试在创造模式下（打开作弊）红石电路和指令等玩法。
2019年5月，《我的世界》击败了《俄罗斯方块》，已售出1.76亿份，成为有史以来最畅销的电子游戏 [48]。2020年，《我的世界》荣获 “2020年儿童选择奖” [44]。2023年10月，《我的世界》销量超过3亿份]。
2024年11月，获得2024金摇杆奖持续游玩奖（PC/主机）。
